TextEng: Who are you?
I'm here to kill you, Geth. Are you ready?
I have silver charms - from Neurik.
Text: 은 부적을 가지고 왔어 - 뉴릭에게서 받은 거야.

TextEng: Me says you tell me your name.
Me kills you, Geth. Now!
Me gots silver charms. They works, yuh!
Text: 나 은 부적 가져왔어. 효과 있어!

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> If you want to change the future, you must do it yourself.
Text: <StartCheck>[통찰]</Start> 미래를 바꾸고 싶다면, 네가 직접 해야 해.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> This charm comes from Neurik. It is safe.
Take the charm, or I'll see you dead myself.
Text: 부적을 받아, 안 그러면 내가 직접 죽일 거야.

TextEng: I don't care. I'm killing you now.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Neurik give charm. Is good!
You gets charm, or me kills you!
Text: 너 부적 받아, 안 그러면 나 너 죽여!

TextEng: Grrr... me kills you now!
What means you? Me not knowing.
Huh? What are you talking about?
How did you become like this?
<StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> I've been sent to end the werewolf menace. If you give me your ring, I will leave and no one will come searching for you in the future.
Text: <StartCheck>[통찰]</Start> 늑대인간 위협을 끝내러 파견됐어. 반지를 주면, 떠날게. 그러면 앞으로 아무도 널 찾지 않을 거야.

TextEng: I'll try to find some help for you. Stay here.
You stays here. Me goes to get help, then come back, okay?
Text: 너 여기 있어. 나 도움 받으러 갔다가 돌아올게, 알았지?

TextEng: What makes you become werewolf?
Do you know where I can find any of them?
Text: 그들을 어디서 찾을 수 있는지 알아?

TextEng: Where me find these people? You know.
Text: 나 이 사람들 어디서 찾아? 너 알아.

TextEng: Excuse me. I will leave.
Me sorry. Me go now.
